						<h2 class="industries-seo-title">
							Cloud Hawk’ approach to software performance testing with technology examples						</h2>
						<div class="industries-seo-arrow">
							<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
								<rect width="48" height="48" fill="#F3F4F4"></rect>
								<path d="M12 30L24 18L36 30" stroke="#1C1E24" stroke-width="3"></path>
